{"tid":1927852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Strong Hold] 歐盟周日宣布限制口罩等防護醫療裝備出口","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T04:57:26.000Z","uid":65166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b25b984b762c4def576b9f7efcf9c55b6e40fd13","tid":1927852,"uid":65166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>德國封5國邊境防疫情擴大 歐盟限制防護醫療裝備出口</strong><br />\n<br />\n歐洲疫情嚴峻，各國紛紛加強控制疫情。<strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">歐盟執委會主席范德賴恩（Ursula von der Leyen）周日宣布限制口罩及防護眼鏡、護目鏡、面罩、口鼻防護裝備、防護服等防護醫療裝備出口，以確保有足夠物資抗疫。</span></strong></strong>她警告道，實施邊境檢查的歐盟國家正在威脅供應鏈，增加物資短缺的風險。德國則是宣布關閉與法國、奧地利、瑞士、丹麥、盧森堡的5國邊界，以控制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n范德賴恩表示，「我們今天通過了防護裝備的出口授權計劃，這代表只有在歐盟政府的明確授權下，此類醫療用品才能出口到非歐盟國家。」她續指，「這是正確的作法，因為我們的醫療保健系統需要這些裝備。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">范德賴恩強調，歐盟成員國之間彼此分享裝備的必要性，並指出如德國與法國實施的出口禁令是適得其反。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德國內政部長錫霍佛（Horst Seehofer）周日表示，將關閉與法國、奧地利、瑞士、丹麥、盧森堡的邊界，以控制疫情。據德國《圖片報》報導，禁令將從當地時間周一早上8時開始實施，貨品與跨境通勤者可豁免，目前僅剩荷蘭與比利時兩國邊境未封鎖。除德國外，丹麥、捷克、波蘭也「封關」或實施嚴格的邊境檢查。<br />\n<br />\n來源：台灣蘋果<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200316/PFSTWWH4SKWH33NFXPUVHGLCJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200316%2FPFSTWWH4SKWH33NFXPUVHGLCJY%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=ec5dd0ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200316%2FPFSTWWH4SKWH33NFXPUVHGLCJY%2F&h=79127bdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200316/PFSTWWH4SKWH33NFXPUVHGLCJY/</a>"},{"pid":"505750027e1d7187961fe6faafb7ecce796c8169","tid":1927852,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4e8d6af1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&h=19bc6c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］有人整左維尼病毒公仔出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926864\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926864</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2798fcbf7059097fb9d19964bb97b54378292052","tid":1927852,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n唔封關等人周圍走？"}]}